original_title: The 3rd Annual Howie Mandel Stand-up Gala
overview: Star-studded special from Montréal’s Just For Laughs Festival features special guest Cedric the Entertainer (The Original Kings of Comedy) and comedy all-stars Cristela Alonzo (CRISTELA), Ron Funches (POWERLESS), Gina Yashere (THE DAILY SHOW), Orny Adams (Comedian), Gad Elmaleh (THE ADVENTURES OF TINTIN), and more
title: The 3rd Annual Howie Mandel Stand-up Gala
